--------------<br>
<br>
Please actually play the class before you make us out to be  gods<br>
<br>
Ever try channeling a lifetap on a mob knocking the shit out of you? FD for that matter also? <br>
<br>
HT? 1001 damage every 72 mins 1501 with Uholy aura at 60. The other HT's you mentioned cost AA points and are on the same timer. Every 72 mins!<br>
<br>
DoT's are relatively crappy and usually not worth the spell slot. Sometimes good to use sometimes not. Theres only 8 spell slots. 6 for most SK's I'd imagine. FD is always memed and assuming most have Harmshield memmed as well. I know I do.<br>
<br>
Our monster weapons? Please go take a gander at our offensive caps. <br>
<br>
In the 50+ world  two handers will do more damage than one handers. Monks know this as well. And in attempt to try to make shields more attractive they upped the bash damage. Makes sense, bashing for 10 with a 50+ AC shield? <br>
<br>
Granted its a fun and diverse class but what do we do in raids?<br>
<br>
Grass is always greener.<br>
<br>
I play a monk also(no I'm not just saying that.) I've lurked around here for quite a while now. I just never posted before. I didn't drop an insane amount of plat on a twink, the lil' leezard was still in full wu's 'till level 43.  <br>
<br>
I didn't make that monk to solo. Hell at the time I made him,about 2 weeks after I first purchased the game in april 01, I didn't even know what  a monk was supposed to do, any class for that matter. I just saw one and thought &quot;wow that looks fun!&quot; And it has been a blast leveling him up, solo and grouping. <br>
<br>
But if you really do enjoy playing your character, be it monk, cleric, ranger, druid (ok I went too far there <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ).  No nerf will keep you from playing them. Just take it in stride, it will come in circles and eventually you'll even back out again. <br>
